Installation instructions
=========================

1) Install dependencies:

- make
- C compiler
- Git (to fetch go packages)
- Go compiler and tools

2) Build:

$ make

To run tests:

$ make tests

To clean up:

$ make clean

3) Run:

$ go/bin/monsti <configuration file>

To run the example site, go to the example site directory (example/)
and run the start script:
$ ./start.sh
Monsti will be listening on localhost:8080

# Problems?

Fill an issue at:
https://github.com/chrneumann/monsti/issues

Thanks and have fun!
